00:00:09.154 --> 00:00:12.533 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Listen, Obey, and Be Blessed.”

00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:14.869 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Are you ready to sing with us?

00:00:27.047 --> 00:00:32.970 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If we have listened to Christ,
will we show it?

00:00:32.970 --> 00:00:39.018 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His teaching shines
as it shows us the way.

00:00:39.018 --> 00:00:44.857 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It makes us happy
to hear and to know it,

00:00:44.857 --> 00:00:51.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But we’ll be blessed
if we know and obey.

00:00:51.780 --> 00:00:57.828 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Listen, obey,
and be blessed

00:00:57.828 --> 00:01:04.001 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
