God’s will expressed.

00:01:04.001 --> 00:01:10.132 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If you’d be happy
and enter his rest,

00:01:10.132 --> 00:01:17.014 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Listen, obey,
and be blessed.

00:01:19.725 --> 00:01:25.773 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our way of life,
like a house, gives protection

00:01:25.773 --> 00:01:31.737 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When it is built on the rock,
not on sand.

00:01:31.737 --> 00:01:37.493 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If we apply
Jesus’ loving direction,

00:01:37.493 --> 00:01:44.208 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll build a life
which on bedrock will stand.

00:01:44.208 --> 00:01:50.297 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Listen, obey,
and be blessed

00:01:50.297 --> 00:01:56.595 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you hear
God’s will expressed.

00:01:56.595 --> 00:02:02.601 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
